{"tid":961844,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone XS Max 褲袋爆炸起火 美國用戶擬向 Apple 興訟","createTime":"2018-12-30T12:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T03:27:08.000Z","uid":52215,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5112c6e4a7756ecfa255cd36190d28fc27241321","tid":961844,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T12:05:48.000Z","msg":"手機是我們生活的一部分，所以每當有手機爆炸起火的消息傳出，特別引起外界關注。最新成為主角的是 iPhone XS Max，這部才上市不久的手機，早前據說在美國俄亥俄一名男子的後褲袋爆炸起火，現在該名苦主正在考慮向 Apple 興訟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97YREby.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97YREby.jpg&h=122d0f5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源：pocketnow<br />\n<br />\n這名不幸的 iPhone XS Max 用戶名叫 J. Hilard，他將手機爆炸起火後的相片傳給網站 iDrop News，他表示事件發生在 12 月 12 日下午約 3 時，他當時在俄亥俄的哥倫布市附近。一陣奇怪的氣味由他的後褲袋傳出，當時 iPhone XS Max 正在褲袋內，與此同時他亦感受到大量的熱力正在灼痛他的皮膚，不出一會手機就冒出黃黃綠綠的煙霧。<br />\n<br />\n由於當時 Hilard 身處的房間內有另一女士，他只好馬上走到另一房間，把自己的鞋和褲盡快脫掉。公司一名高層聽到 Hilard 的慘叫聲後，衝入房間協助以滅火筒將 iPhone 的火撲熄。他將起火的 iPhone 帶到 Apple Store 後，對方建議安排一換一，而起火的手機則交由 Apple 的工程團隊檢查，但 Hilard 拒絕 Apple 的安排。他將手機帶回家後再致電 Apple Care，最終 Hilard 要求 Apple 就他的衣物和鞋，連同因為無法使用手機期間的通訊費用，向他作出賠償。<br />\n<br />\n來源：pocketnow"},{"pid":"4a7d2518ee6f9dac7ca6b297454571d69a83382d","tid":961844,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T03:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> apple五十步笑百步"},{"pid":"b27e5c3dc13cf720a8f8008588a9bbcd6d15bdbf","tid":961844,"uid":57674,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T05:26:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">而起火的手機則交由 Apple 的工程團隊檢查，但 Hilard 拒絕 Apple 的安排</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c39633ebc23c54327dfa19b405d4fdbb08da961","tid":961844,"uid":164092,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"b27e5c3dc13cf720a8f8008588a9bbcd6d15bdbf","tid":961844,"uid":57674,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T05:26:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">而起火的手機則交由 Apple 的工程團隊檢查，但 Hilard 拒絕 Apple 的安排</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"正常都拒絕啦，俾咗佢，佢話咩都得，唔會俾返部機你，之前d idog笑人蠢，話點解要俾返部機Samsung，同一情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9053d1cdcb330a75e1552ff4298c821eab3cf0ea","tid":961844,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b27e5c3dc13cf720a8f8008588a9bbcd6d15bdbf","tid":961844,"uid":57674,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T05:26:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">而起火的手機則交由 Apple 的工程團隊檢查，但 Hilard 拒絕 Apple 的安排</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T14:11:35.000Z","msg":"梗係搵第三方check啦"},{"pid":"9a7d5a2238266274ddc503284459f5c0038457e0","tid":961844,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T15:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f730c281eaf861d360456f5a69cd096cc513be","tid":961844,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T15:53:37.000Z","msg":"依家iphone都可能爆<br />\n華為贏到開巷<br />\n中或最贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef8dc253192aac35dff4dc8294c22b7e993b0b9","tid":961844,"uid":5134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}